headline: REXR Leases 1.9M Square Feet, Disposes $32M, Grows Rental Rates in QTD
summary: Rexford executes 1.9M sq. ft. of leases, posts 30% comparable rent growth, completes $32M in sales and authorizes a new $500M share repurchase plan.

headline: SL Green to Strengthen Portfolio With Acquisition of 346 Madison Avenue
summary: SLG is set to acquire 346 Madison Avenue and a neighboring site at 11 East 44th Street for $160M.
